    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Multiple elements of this theme can use specific fonts if they are available. To download the required fonts, you can add the file [additional_fonts.css](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/blob/main/snippets/additional_fonts.css) to your [snippets folder](https://help.obsidian.md/Extending+Obsidian/CSS+snippets). This file can be very heavy. If you don't plan on using all of them, I would recommend deleting the unecessary @font-face from the snippet. You can see how which font is used [in the doc](https://elsatam.github.io/obsidian-fancy-a-story/docs/stylesettings/stylesettings.html#additional-fonts)",
      "target": "此主题的多个元素可以使用特定字体（如果可用）。要下载所需字体，您可以将文件 [additional_fonts.css](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/blob/main/snippets/additional_fonts.css) 添加到您的 [snippets 文件夹](https://help.obsidian.md/Extending+Obsidian/CSS+snippets)。此文件可能非常大。如果您不打算使用所有字体，我建议从代码片段中删除不必要的 @font-face。您可以在[文档](https://elsatam.github.io/obsidian-fancy-a-story/docs/stylesettings/stylesettings.html#additional-fonts)中查看哪些字体被使用。"
    },
    {
      "type": "title",
