      "target": "画布节点标签"
    },
    {
      "type": "description",
      "source": "Usage of tags to define specific styling for canvas card can be very powerful. However, it requires a code that can cause performance issues. Also, such styling come as independant snippets. You can add the file [canvas-node-bundle](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/blob/main/snippets/canvas/canvas-node-bundle.css) to your [snippets folder](https://help.obsidian.md/Extending+Obsidian/CSS+snippets) to download all the effects. Or choose individual ones from [this list](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/tree/main/snippets/canvas).",
      "target": "使用标签来定义画布卡片的特定样式非常强大。但是，它需要的代码可能会导致性能问题。此外，此类样式作为独立的代码片段提供。您可以将文件 [canvas-node-bundle](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/blob/main/snippets/canvas/canvas-node-bundle.css) 添加到您的 [snippets 文件夹](https://help.obsidian.md/Extending+Obsidian/CSS+snippets) 以下载所有效果。或者从[此列表](https://github.com/ElsaTam/obsidian-fancy-a-story/tree/main/snippets/canvas)中选择单独的效果。"
